sub_title: Master of Biomedical Sciences (Toxicology & Human Pathobiology)
summary: First, I had a bachelor degree in Pharmacy and more than 6 years of experience as a Pharmacist. Then, I realized that I need to continue further with my study and hence I joined Radboud University and successfully finished my masters degree in Biomedical sciences (Toxicology and Human Pathobiology).  Due to the fact that I have an intense interest to be a research scientist, I would like to pursue PhD in biomedical or related field. Please contact me at tesfana2000@gmail.com.
